    "root_cause": "Inject 60-second outbound delay on the HSS (PyHSS). The HSS container is running, the process is alive, and the IP is reachable \u2014 but all Diameter responses are delayed by 60 seconds, far exceeding the Cx Diameter timeout. Tests how the I-CSCF and S-CSCF handle a Diameter peer that accepts connections but never responds in time.",
